%N A001348 Mersenne numbers: 2^p - 1, where p is prime.
%C A001348 Mersenne numbers A000225 whose indices are primes. - _Omar E. Pol_, Aug 31 2008
%C A001348 All terms are of the form 4k-1. - _Paul Muljadi_, Jan 31 2011
